  "commit_message": "Linux SslStream: custom BIO_METHOD over managed buffer windows (#128245)\n\n## Summary\n\nReplace the two `BIO_s_mem` instances backing each SSL handle on Linux\nwith a custom `BIO_METHOD` that operates on **caller-supplied managed\nbuffer windows**, and refactor the Linux PAL so every SSL operation\n(`SSL_do_handshake`, `SSL_write`, `SSL_read`) is wrapped in a single\nP/Invoke that installs the windows, runs the SSL call, and tears them\ndown. Combined, these changes:\n\n- eliminate the BIO staging memcpy",
